The paper proposes two novel approaches for the early detection of sepsis using deep learning and data mining techniques. The methods involve the use of temporal convolutional networks and dynamic time warping for time series classification. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
